data.description: Motivated to sell... This 5 Bedroom home features soaring ceilings, open floor plan and endless spaces for the entire family. Designer Wood Tile, carpet and tile throughout. Window seating in the dining area, perfect for any shape or size of table. The kitchen features double ovens, gas cook top and pot filler, huge walk in pantry.  And a perfectly appointed pocket office just off the kitchen. Outdoor stone fireplace over looking a pond.  Luxurious primary bedroom with sitting area, entrance to the covered patio. Frameless shower, endless counter space, dual sinks, and a huge walk in closet. Oversized game and media room with all the media room equipment needed.  Second level bedrooms feature quaint sitting areas. Private study perfect for home office with glass french doors. Back covered porch is perfect for an outdoor living or dining area.   Main living room boasts a beautiful floor to ceiling white stone fireplace complete with gas logs.
